MAINTAINER Rapid 7 - InsightOps <InsightOpsTeam@rapid7.com>

WORKDIR /usr/src/app

RUN npm install --production
COPY index.js /usr/src/app/index.js

ENTRYPOINT ["/usr/src/app/index.js"]
CMD []
